23:36.334 --> 23:37.918
When can we have sex?

23:37.960 --> 23:39.170
LUCILLE:
After Cinco.

23:39.212 --> 23:40.921
Cinco?

23:40.963 --> 23:43.549
LUCILLE: Just get a boat ready,
we'll make our getaway.

23:43.590 --> 23:45.467
So not... not today.

23:45.509 --> 23:49.013
<i>And that's when she saw Michael</i>
<i>for the first time</i>

23:49.055 --> 23:51.391
<i>since the last time</i>
<i>he left the family.</i>

23:51.432 --> 23:52.766
Wow.

23:52.808 --> 23:54.227
This is a step up from prison.

23:54.268 --> 23:55.811
How would you know?

23:55.853 --> 23:57.397
You haven't come
to visit me once.

23:57.438 --> 23:58.398
Yeah. Sorry.

23:58.439 --> 23:59.815
I feel bad about that.

23:59.857 --> 24:01.483
So you're here to make amends?

24:01.525 --> 24:04.070
Because you know your mother
will always take you back.

24:04.111 --> 24:06.655
And because
I know my mother wants me

24:06.697 --> 24:08.949
to sign away any connection
to the family business.

24:08.991 --> 24:09.951
I just need a signature.

24:09.992 --> 24:11.535
I'm happy to help.
If...

24:11.577 --> 24:13.871
- you do something for me.
- For me.

24:13.913 --> 24:16.207
Yeah, I heard
that's been happening.

24:16.249 --> 24:18.459
I'm happy to help you, honey.

24:18.500 --> 24:20.461
Me, too.

24:20.502 --> 24:23.172
<i>And that's how Michael got his</i>
<i>mother's rights to the movie.</i>

24:23.214 --> 24:25.716
<i>But not right away.</i>

24:37.019 --> 24:38.104
So happy to help.

24:38.145 --> 24:39.105
Me, too.

24:39.146 --> 24:41.523
- So, everything else is good?
- Yeah.

24:41.565 --> 24:44.026
You've talked to your sister,
the radical?

24:44.068 --> 24:46.070
Yeah. She's a redhead now,
and she's dating Herbert Love,

24:46.112 --> 24:47.863
but other than her looks
and her belief system,

24:47.905 --> 24:49.365
- Oh...
