24:49.407 --> 24:52.243
So that's Lindsay in the photo.

24:52.285 --> 24:53.953
And I hear you're dating
an actress...

24:53.994 --> 24:55.455
who's also dating Ron Howard?

24:55.496 --> 24:56.456
(wry laugh)

24:56.497 --> 24:57.998
No, no...
no, no, no, no, no, no.

24:58.040 --> 25:00.167
She is not dating
Ron Howard, Mother.

25:00.209 --> 25:01.449
Ron Howard is her father, okay?

25:01.461 --> 25:02.878
(Michael chuckles)

25:02.920 --> 25:04.922
Your mind...

25:04.964 --> 25:07.091
I did, though, actually
find out who she is dating.

25:07.133 --> 25:09.093
<i>Michael had found out,</i>
<i>earlier that day,</i>

25:09.135 --> 25:11.553
<i>when he visited</i>
<i>her apartment to head off</i>

25:11.595 --> 25:15.182
<i>any ill feelings</i>
<i>she might have about this...</i>

25:15.224 --> 25:16.642
I'll do everything
in my power to make sure

25:16.683 --> 25:17.851
she never dates you again.

25:17.893 --> 25:18.894
<i>Or this...</i>

25:18.936 --> 25:20.146
You are ruining
my life, Ron Howard!

25:20.187 --> 25:21.314
Nice, right?

25:21.355 --> 25:22.773
Is too big.

25:22.815 --> 25:25.067
She likes small.

25:25.109 --> 25:26.986
LEM:
Can I please have ice cream?

25:27.027 --> 25:30.197
No, no, you are a Depardieu.
No sweets.

25:30.239 --> 25:32.283
Getting excited about Cinco?

25:32.325 --> 25:35.661
Your Cinco, not ours.

25:38.705 --> 25:42.084
<i>Michael wasn't proud</i>
<i>of what he was about to do.</i>

25:42.126 --> 25:44.170
Hey, Lem, I can reach
the ice cream and, you know,

25:44.211 --> 25:45.671
in my family,
we play a game called

25:45.712 --> 25:49.383
"If You Do Something For Me."

25:49.425 --> 25:50.884
Rules are meant
to be broken, huh?

25:50.926 --> 25:54.054
I will give you this Dove bar,
if you do something for me.

25:54.096 --> 25:55.389
We have Dove bars?

25:55.431 --> 25:57.183
We do. Look at that.

25:57.224 --> 26:01.187
Tell me what you know
about this "George Maharis."

26:01.228 --> 26:02.146
Not much.

26:02.188 --> 26:03.230
He's old.

26:03.272 --> 26:04.565
Is he older than me?

26:04.606 --> 26:05.816
A few years.

26:05.858 --> 26:07.193
He looks like you.

26:08.277 --> 26:10.154
So, handsome.

26:10.196 --> 26:12.532
<i>And that's when Lucille</i>
<i>found a way</i>

26:12.573 --> 26:14.408
<i>to keep the brothers</i>
<i>from colluding.</i>

26:14.450 --> 26:16.076
George Maharis.

26:16.118 --> 26:18.078
George--
that's your brother's name.

26:18.120 --> 26:19.663
George Oscar Bluth.

26:19.705 --> 26:23.376
Yes, uh, George
is Gob's first name, yep.

26:23.417 --> 26:24.751
<i>And that's when Michael</i>

26:24.793 --> 26:26.712
<i>remembered something else</i>
<i>strange.</i>

26:30.216 --> 26:32.176
I probably should have
expected that.

26:32.218 --> 26:33.177
<i>And then stranger...</i>

26:33.219 --> 26:35.012
MICHAEL:
"Love each other..."

26:35.054 --> 26:37.139
Oh, that definitely
sounds like Gob.

26:37.181 --> 26:39.975
<i>And he did say he was</i>
<i>seeing someone famous...</i>

26:40.017 --> 26:41.435
