32:56.894 --> 32:58.604
<i>Tobias boards the boat</i>

32:58.645 --> 33:00.731
<i>originally meant</i>
<i>for Lucille's escape,</i>

33:00.773 --> 33:04.484
<i>and after making one stop,</i>
<i>faces the awful truth.</i>

33:04.526 --> 33:08.029
They're going to be talking
about this bomb for years.

33:08.071 --> 33:10.323
TOBIAS:
Oh, God, it is bad, isn't it?

33:10.365 --> 33:12.534
Lindsay was right
to discourage me.

33:14.369 --> 33:16.413
- Tobias?
- Marky?

33:16.455 --> 33:18.498
If you're not Lindsay,
then where is Lindsay?

33:18.540 --> 33:19.959
Isn't that her
on the love boat?

33:20.000 --> 33:22.628
- But I just put a bomb on the love boat!
- What?!

33:22.669 --> 33:24.189
- Lindsay! Lindsay!
- Lindsay! Lindsay!

33:24.212 --> 33:25.505
Lindsay, there's a bomb!

33:28.383 --> 33:29.342
<i>Lindsay remembers</i>
<i>she's on a boat...</i>

33:29.384 --> 33:30.260
Oh, (bleep)

33:30.302 --> 33:32.345
<i>...that Marky had intended</i>
<i>to bomb.</i>

33:32.387 --> 33:34.097
You gotta get off the boat!

33:34.139 --> 33:35.515
<i>And it turns out</i>
<i>to be kind of romantic.</i>

33:35.557 --> 33:37.244
Bomb!

33:38.393 --> 33:39.435
(whoops)

33:39.555 --> 33:43.565
<i>...that Lindsay and Tobias</i>
<i>have matching suitcases.</i>

